<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2024-10-01T17:01:28-04:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2024-10-01T17:01:28-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-01T17:01:28-04:00</updated><title>下一代 iPhone SE 可能会失去 home 键，添加 Face ID 和 Apple Intelligence</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;直立放在桌子上的 iPhone 14。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/T6Y32Q-Wlup_D3jDuqIks4Ozwkg=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73625220/226270_IPHONE_14_REGULAR_PHO_阿克拉莱斯_0657.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;iPhone 14，下一代 iPhone SE 可能看起来很像。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Amelia Holowaty Krales / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;EtL48V&quot;>;一款感觉非常像任何其他现代非预算 iPhone 的 iPhone SE 显然将于明年初推出，&lt;a href =&quot;https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/apple-readies-iphone-se-4-upgraded-ipad-air-for-early-2025&quot;>;根据&lt;em>;彭博社&lt;/em>;的马克·古尔曼&lt;/a>;。该手机将使用 Face ID，并且能够运行 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/10/24175405/wwdc-apple-ai-news-features-ios-18-macos -15-iphone-ipad-mac&quot;>;Apple Intelligence&lt;/a>;，他今天重申。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;5hwHsF&quot;>;新款 iPhone SE 型号可能支持 Apple Intelligence &lt;a href=&quot;https: //www.theverge.com/2024/8/11/24217924/iphone-se-apple-intelligence-support-generative-ai-rumor&quot;>;说了很多关于他们的表现&lt;/a>; - 这需要&lt;a href= “https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/12/24219823/apple-intelligence-gemini-copilot-ai-iphone-16-pro-pixel-9-ram&quot;>;大量内存&lt;/a>;例如，运行本地人工智能功能。预计它们看起来会像 iPhone 14，取消厚实的顶部和底部边框以及主页按钮；两者都是入门级智能手机的首创。还有传言称 iPhone SE 4 将&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/3/24234749/apple-iphone-se-4th- Generation-oled-display-rumor-leak&quot; >;获取 OLED 屏幕&lt;/a>;，而不是通常的 LCD。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;9Pu3LU&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem -component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Apple 的下一代 iPhone SE 可能会升级 OLED&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge .com/2024/9/3/24234749/apple-iphone-se-4th- Generation-oled-display-rumor-leak&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;下一代 iPhone SE 可能拥有 Apple Intelligence，这说明了很多&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/11/24217924/iphone-se-apple-intelligence-support-generative-ai-rumor&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>; &lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;F75v4E&quot;>;苹果将在...生产 11 英寸和 13 英寸 iPad Air，并进行“内部改进”&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https ://www.theverge.com/2024/10/1/24259713/iphone-se-face-id-apple-intelligence-no-home-button&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/1/24259713/iphone-se-face-id-apple-intelligence-no-home-button" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/1/24259713/iphone-se-face-id-apple-intelligence-no-home-button</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-01T16:52:13-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-01T16:52:13-04:00</updated><title>现在最值得购买的健身追踪器</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Apple Watch、Garmin Epix、Fitbit 和 Amazfit Bip 健身追踪器采用风格化的蓝色背景。&quot; src =“https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/9NfU5CzAkm1H45234kKpT8gicKk=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/70657030/acastro_220321_5092_0001。 0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;照片插图由 Alex Castro / The Verge 拍摄&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;从简单的健身手环和坚固耐用的运动手表到戒指，这些都是您可以获得的最佳追踪器。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt; a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/22985108/best-fitness-tracker&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/22985108/best-fitness-tracker" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/22985108/best-fitness-tracker</id><author><name>宋茜</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-01T16:46:36-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-01T16:46:36-04:00</updated><title> Nvidia 的一体化应用程序将于今年晚些时候取代 GeForce Experience</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Ndivia 徽标的矢量拼贴画。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/wXbeKJWcUChKmG6SH82OfB1DyAc=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73625166/STK083_B_NVIDIA_C.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Cath Virginia / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;PFSeRR&quot;>;Nvidia 的 GPU 测试版应用程序即将推出&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024 /8/6/24213585/nvidia-app-update-rtx-video-display-features&quot;>;其完整发布之旅&lt;/a>;，该公司表示打算“&lt;a href=&quot;https:// go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nvidia.com%2Fen-us%2Fgeforce%2Fnews%2Fnvidia-app-beta-update-g-sync-controls- rtx-hdr-multi-monitor%2F&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F10%2F1%2F24259664%2Fnvidia-app-beta-replace-geforce-experience- control-panel&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;在年底前将所有剩余的 GeForce Experience 用户迁移&lt;/a>;”到新应用。今天，Nvidia 添加了更多功能以使应用程序做好准备，包括打开和关闭 G-Sync 的功能、对 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/1/ 的多显示器支持24/24048892/nvidia-rtx-video-hdr-feature-ai&quot;>;RTX HDR&lt;/a>;，以及驱动程序回滚。该应用程序现在还可以通知您是否正在播放可能阻止您的 DRM 内容 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2013/5/23/4358300/nvidia-shadowplay-and-geforce-gtx-780 &quot;>;ShadowPlay 录制&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;1V1yDQ&quot;>;Nvidia 表示，即将推出的应用程序更新还将引入 Nvidia 控制面板的其余功能，例如环绕声选项、自定义分辨率和多重功能。 - 监视器设置。很快，GeForce Experience 应用程序和 Nvidia 控制面板都将被替换...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/1/24259664/ nvidia-app-beta-replace-geforce-experience-control-panel&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/1/24259664/nvidia-app-beta-replace-geforce-experience-control-panel" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/1/24259664/nvidia-app-beta-replace-geforce-experience-control-panel</id><author><name>奥马尔·沙基尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-01T16:07:50-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-01T16:07:50-04:00</updated><title>这些盒子将通过您家的电源线发送杜比全景声 (Dolby Atmos)</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;并排图像显示 Fasetto 通过电力线发射器和接收器发出的声音。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/517FXZ27WRGRcb14oCu1tOb0l1A=/0x0:945x630/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73625078/audiocu.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Fasetto 的 Audio Cu 通过家庭现有的电源线将音频信号发送到环绕声扬声器。&lt;/em>; |图片：Fasetto&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;hWktDd&quot;>;Fasetto 宣布其 Audio Cu 系统可使用家中现有的电源线将电视和其他音频设备连接到扬声器和低音炮。 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20241001844031/en/Fasetto-Inc.-Earns-a-Dolby-Atmos%C2%AE-Product-Certification-for-Its-Sound-电力线上方-首页-音频-解决方案-音频-Cu/?feedref=JjAwJuNHiystnCoBq_hl-Q-tiwWZwkcswR1UZtV7eGe24xL9TZOyQUMS3J72mJlQ7fxFuNFTHSunhvli30RlBNXya2izy9YOgHlBiZQk2LOzmn6JePCpHPC iYGaEx4DL1Rq8pNwkf3AarimpDzQGuQ==&quot;>;获得杜比实验室的杜比全景声产品认证&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id =&quot;tKnz7n&quot;>;类似于电力线网络解决方案，可以利用现有的电线&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23715458/ethernet-hardwire-home-wireless-internet-powerline-networking-how-为了“在家中共享互联网”，Fasetto 的 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.audiocu.com/&quot;>;Audio Cu&lt;/a>; 是一种替代方案，无需将音频线穿过墙壁或尝试将连接扬声器与音频源的电线隐藏在地毯和家具下。它也是 Wi-Fi 或蓝牙等无线解决方案的替代方案，后者有自己的挑战和妥协，包括增加的延迟、音频压缩和信号可靠性。&lt;/p>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;cite>;我...&lt;/cite>;&lt;/figure>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/1/24259598/fasetto-dolby-atmos-audio-cu-speakers-电源线&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/1/24259598/fasetto-dolby-atmos-audio-cu-speakers-power-lines" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/1/24259598/fasetto-dolby-atmos-audio-cu-speakers-power-lines</id><author><name>安德鲁·利泽夫斯基</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-01T15:33:03-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-01T15:33:03-04:00</updated><title> YouTube TV 可能很快就能让你在无法观看的情况下继续收听</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;红色、黑色和奶油色几何背景上的红色 YouTube 徽标图像&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/JBEqOijelzK7BoccqsVpZWVlIS8=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/ cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73625006/acastro_STK092_03.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;由 Alex Castro / The Verge 绘制的插图&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;dqQYgW&quot;>;即使您无法观看，很快您就可以继续在 YouTube TV 上收听电视节目了。 Google 似乎终于在其 &lt;a href=&quot;https://tv.youtube.com/welcome/&quot;>;YouTube TV 流媒体服务&lt;/a>;中引入了后台播放功能。该公司向 &lt;em>;The Verge&lt;/em>; 证实，它正在“试验”在手机锁定后启用 YouTube TV 播放。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;aB2gCV&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://9to5google.com/2024/10/01/youtube-tv-gets-background-play/&quot;>;据 9to5Google 报道&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;，该功能是在几周前被 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.reddit.com/r/youtubetv/comments/1fhnj30/background_play/&quot;>;Reddit 用户&lt;/ a>; 他们发现，即使将视频应用程序发送到移动设备上的后台，他们也可以继续收听 YouTube TV 音频。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;IHi5jM&quot;>;后台播放可让您在手机屏幕关闭或锁定时继续收听内容。因此，即使您无法观看动作，您仍然可以收听音频。这可能会有所帮助...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/1/24259647/youtube-tv-app-background-playback-google- ios-android&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/1/24259647/youtube-tv-app-background-playback-google-ios-android" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/1/24259647/youtube-tv-app-background-playback-google-ios-android</id><author><name>詹妮弗·帕蒂森·图伊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-01T15:23:14-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-01T15:23:14-04:00</updated><title>主题让您有更多时间编辑帖子</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;显示 Threads 徽标的图像&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/OF-7U-mE2ciQD-6oFZtb7FgmHiA=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox -cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73624978/STK156_Instagram_threads_3.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：边缘&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;GfScD1&quot;>;您现在有 &lt;a href =&quot;https://www.threads.net/@mosseri/post/DAltcc9v1ye/?xmt=AUFiUGxxRkM4SUxsV2RPZThfTkh5UzJ3V2NjRlNMRXRxM3RISjNITjJjcEVD&quot;>;在 Threads 上编辑帖子需要 15 分钟&lt;/a>;，较之前的五分钟限制有所增加。如果您打开了 fediverse 共享，这意味着您必须等待 15 分钟，您的帖子才会显示在 Mastodon 和其他平台上。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;8vtJvU&quot;>;与其他平台。例如，X 允许您&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/6/6/23751962/twitter-edit-tweet-limit-extended-60-minutes-blue-subscribers&quot;>;编辑您的帖子最多一小时&lt;/a>;，但您必须付费订阅。 Mastodon 还&lt;a href=&quot;https://fedi.tips/how-do-i-edit-posts-in-mastodon/&quot;>;让您可以在帖子发布后随时免费编辑帖子&lt;/a>;已发布。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;183oDQ&quot;>;此外，Threads 现在可以让您看到谁关注您并喜欢来自其他 Fediverse 服务器（例如 Mastodon）的帖子。无论人们使用什么平台，这都将使跟踪新关注者和参与度变得更加容易......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/ 10/1/24259606/threads-post-time-limit-fediverse&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/1/24259606/threads-post-time-limit-fediverse" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/1/24259606/threads-post-time-limit-fediverse</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-01T14:59:20-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-01T14:59:20-04:00</updated><title> Sleep Number 最新智能床旨在解决盗汗问题</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/LEHRXhCdVQO3Pz_wpn7KQLOk0ZA=/711x757:3306x2487/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73624937 /cc_FT_FXT_FX2_2407_01a.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;ClimateCool 智能床具有可调节床垫硬度、睡眠跟踪、灵活底座和主动冷却技术。&lt;/em>; |图片：Sleep Number&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;uCv7vx&quot;>;Sleep Number 最新的智能床旨在让您在夜间保持凉爽。 &lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sleepnumber.com%2Fproducts%2Fclimatecool&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref= https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F10%2F1%2F24259440%2Fsleep-number-climate-cool-smart-bed-price-features&quot; rel=&quot;赞助 nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;ClimateCool智能床&lt;/a>;起价 5,499 美元，是该公司以可调节床垫硬度而闻名的最新产品。在&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20240930057916/en/Sleep-Number-Introduces-ClimateCool%E2%84%A2-Smart-Bed-Actively-Cools-and-Effortless-调整为更深更舒适的睡眠/?feedref=JjAwJuNHiystnCoBq_hl-bsjWlVyeNLyq_m2tvaHJJaD1w08bW43U_zsPK9s38B4rCOi9QzgjCezTS3Nw_X6kJUrpSBm-Hav1w-UkdSlG3miu0ZZ-LtXj CwD3Ec3ldN_zZCGORvG0LE20YOvo49uqw==&quot;>;新闻稿&lt;/a>;，该公司表示新床垫可以让你的身体保持在最佳温度其“有科学支持”的降温计划可能会引起患有更年期症状的人们特别感兴趣。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;af2Eww&quot;>;这是 Sleep Number 的第二张智能床，可在床的两侧提供单独的温度控制。 &lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sleepnumber.com%2Fproducts%2Fclimate360&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref= https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F10%2F1%2F24259440%2Fsleep-number-climate-cool-smart-bed-price-features&quot; rel=&quot;赞助 nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Climate360 &lt;/a>; 于 2020 年推出，同样可以主动吸走身体热量，帮助您保持凉爽，但与 ClimateCool 不同的是，如果您晚上太冷，它也可以让您暖和起来。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;R7PsNr&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{ &quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Sleep Number 终于推出了一款价格实惠的智能床垫&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/17/24180247/sleep-number-c1- smart-bed-8-sleep-smart-home&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;jzi6nb&quot;>;但是...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/1/24259440/sleep-number-climate-cool-smart-bed-price-features&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/1/24259440/sleep-number-climate-cool-smart-bed-price-features" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/1/24259440/sleep-number-climate-cool-smart-bed-price-features</id><author><name>詹妮弗·帕蒂森·图伊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-01T14:54:03-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-01T14:54:03-04:00</updated><title>最好的 iPhone</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;带有图形背景的各种型号的 iPhone 16。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/52vtvsLAoZdwZwYEDPCaqUbQUUw=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72025718/247288_iPhone_Buying_Guides_2_CVirginia.5 .jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;人工智能时代的新 iPhone。&lt;/em>; |图片：Cath Virginia / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;无论您想要续航数天的电池还是最优惠的价格，我们都为您提供了一些您会喜欢的 iPhone 推荐。&lt;/p >; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23618862/best-iphone-camera-battery-screen-guide&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23618862/best-iphone-camera-battery-screen-guide" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23618862/best-iphone-camera-battery-screen-guide</id><author><name>艾莉森·约翰逊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-01T14:27:20-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-01T14:27:20-04:00</updated><title>在亚马逊 10 月 Prime Day 促销之前您可以获得的最佳优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;位于床头柜上的 Echo Spot 的照片。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/dxw_O3lR3BrUbISSg4lxGH_zZ08=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73599396/247196_Echo_Spot_Review_8A0A151 1_CVirginia.10.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;目前，当您以 44.99 美元购买打折的 Echo Spot 时，亚马逊将免费赠送一个智能灯泡。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Jennifer Pattison Tuohy / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;Ne8kSK&quot;>;如果您错过了这条新闻，亚马逊 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9 /17/24244180/amazon-october-prime-day-big-deal-days-fall-dates-2024&quot;>;最近宣布了秋季第二次 Prim